flowRoot.flowPara: Danielle Black spends her days in the community of Norwood working to build a stronger home for her friends and family. Her career and education embodies what it means to be a leader with an inquisitive mind. Danielle's work—in academia and in the local community—has always focused on education of everyone around her. A vote for Danielle is a vote for unity, transparency, and growth for Norwood.
